##  Summary
This week’s lab successfully demonstrated:
- Control of layout using **box model, positioning, and float/clear**.
- Integration of all concepts into a single cohesive webpage.
- Exposure of layout errors when misapplied (e.g., missing `clear`).
- Proper documentation and organization for submission.

All files (`index.html`, `styles.css`, and screenshots) have been pushed to GitHub in the `week-04/` folder on the same day of the lab session.
